# Canonical Commands Gate

Use ONLY commands defined in @docs/project-config.md.

Minimum set per PR:
- Install
- Lint
- Typecheck (if applicable)
- Test
- Build

If API exists:
- OpenAPI validate command

If schemas exist:
- JSON Schema validate command

If Supabase used:
- Ensure access control tests exist for owner-only / role-based behavior.
